{
  "title": "Segment 3 - GitHub as the front door",
  "locked": false,
  "description": "High-level 3 minute BDM demo showing the GitHub Copilot app as the front door to a connected AI developer ecosystem across GitHub, CLI, SDK, VS Code, and Microsoft Foundry.",
  "rows": [
